e check out. Apperently my bank took a fee giving me 3 EUR left.

As my card wouldnt work I told them to put the stuff aside as I didnt have any other payment options and apologized for the inconveniance. This woman behind me told me she wanted to pay for it.

I had to really push myself to not start crying there and then, and I could tell she understood my frustration. She just said "we've all been there. pay it forward in the future".

I expressed my greatest gratitude and walked out of the store with my food.

On the 30 min walk home I couldn't stop crying, luckily no one saw me.

Any gesture can mean the world to someone in need. I cant even describe how much this woman means to me. I feel like what she did made my entire decade.

Take care of yourself out there, be nice to each others.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/EO8seB3</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[jockeeeeeeee]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Checks out</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/SOtWc31</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WUAZz4T.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/SOtWc31</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[qwertdeep]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>A complete rainbow</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/GU6aG4D</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MwU66Km.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/GU6aG4D</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[WestNord]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Superior cut of Twilight</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/NWGb0vh</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yI8PwLm.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Snapchat filters. Gone too far or not far enough?</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/NWGb0vh</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[UncleToot]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Wait for it.....</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/WtTQ4KP</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pnx94VU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The right, with their love of cancel culture, is sure to be calling for the obliteration of "The Simpsons" after last night's episode, "Poorhouse Rock", dropped a nuclear sized bomb on right wing politics.  It was beautiful and scary.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/WtTQ4KP</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DCon101]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>6 Month Update [128lbs -&gt; 155lbs]</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/mMGeczR</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img al